  "notes": "Born Dec 5, 1839 in Ohio. Father Nathaniel DuBois (1798-1844) died in Kentucky when Rachel was 4. Mother Catharine Eliza Degroff (1802-). Sister Mary DuBois (1841, PA). Brother Barnet DuBois (1833-1872). Married Thomas A. Mayes Mar 24, 1870 in Louisville, KY. Lived in Clark County and Owen County, Indiana. Six children: Catherine M. (1871-1934), Mary Esther (1872-1957), Thomas A. Jr (1875-1933), Morse O. (1876), Samuel H. (1878), Liggan A. (1880-1933). Died Feb 23, 1890 in Champaign County, OH at age 50. Buried in Urbana, OH."
